  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Pierogi</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Pierogi</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Type#Meat\" title=\"Food Type\">Meat</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">Item</a> cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Value#Egg_Value\" title=\"Food Value\">Egg</a>, more than 0.25 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Value#Meat_Value\" title=\"Food Value\">Meat Units</a> and more than 0.25 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Value#Vegetable_Value\" title=\"Food Value\">Vegetable Units</a>. It takes 20 seconds to cook.\n</p><p>Adding 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Food\" title=\"Monster Food\">Monster Foods</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a>. Adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a>. Adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a>.\n</p><p>In <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> using <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pepper\" title=\"Pepper\">Pepper</a> as the vegetable or filler will instead result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stuffed_Pepper_Poppers\" title=\"Stuffed Pepper Poppers\">Stuffed Pepper Poppers</a>.\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot(NoMoleworm).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot%28NoMoleworm%29.png?959309\" width=\"565\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs_Crock_Pot.png?afac2d\" width=\"175\" height=\"82\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot%28No_Mandrake%29.png?2138af\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats.png?6eb40d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Filler cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Cap\" title=\"Red Cap\"><img alt=\"Red Cap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Cap.png?468bf1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/24px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a> A recipe for Pierogi that extenuates a lot of useful hunger value.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morsel\" title=\"Morsel\"><img alt=\"Morsel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Morsel.png?fe6bb2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carrot\" title=\"Carrot\"><img alt=\"Carrot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Carrot.png?e11b81\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Kelp_Fronds.png?cb9519\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ripe_Stone_Fruit\" title=\"Ripe Stone Fruit\"><img alt=\"Ripe Stone Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ripe_Stone_Fruit.png?4eade1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ripe_Stone_Fruit\" title=\"Ripe Stone Fruit\"><img alt=\"Ripe Stone Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ripe_Stone_Fruit.png?4eade1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cactus_Flesh\" title=\"Cactus Flesh\"><img alt=\"Cactus Flesh.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cactus_Flesh.png?e88fdd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cactus_Flower\" title=\"Cactus Flower\"><img alt=\"Cactus Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cactus_Flower.png?61617a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Small_Eggs\" title=\"Small Eggs\"><img alt=\"Small Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Small_Eggs.png?458a05\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Small_Eggs\" title=\"Small Eggs\"><img alt=\"Small Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Small_Eggs.png?458a05\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\"><img alt=\"Pierogi.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pierogi.png?18e74a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Pierogi replenish as much hunger as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Nuggets\" title=\"Honey Nuggets\">Honey Nuggets</a>, but heal for a substantial amount of health (40 health, 10 more than <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Poultice\" title=\"Honey Poultice\">Honey Poultice</a>). It requires Eggs from a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Birdcage\" title=\"Birdcage\">Birdcage</a>, which is relatively resource-intensive to craft (or a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tallbird_Egg\" title=\"Tallbird Egg\">Tallbird Egg</a>, although there are better uses for it), which means it can take a while before one is able to reliably make this recipe, but it can easily become a source of healing for a well-prepared survivor.</li>\n<li>Pierogi have an exceptional spoilage time of 20 days, which makes them a good alternative for Honey Poultice while making long expeditions, or if one needs to increase the longevity of their meat stock.\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bacon_and_Eggs\" title=\"Bacon and Eggs\">Bacon and Eggs</a> have an identical spoilage time and can be made with almost the same recipe (substituting a Vegetable with an Egg), though it restores twice the hunger at the cost of half the health. As such, Bacon and Eggs are better for expeditions where one will expect to take some damage, but still require filling a half-empty belly.</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>During the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Fiesta\" title=\"Pig Fiesta\">Pig Fiesta</a> event in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, Pierogi take on a more festive appearance, resembling <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dumpling#East_Asian\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Dumpling\">steamed dumplings</a>.</li>\n<li>In Poland, &quot;Pierogi&quot; is a dish similar to the Asian dumplings. The Pierogi image in the <i>Don&#x27;t Starve</i> game files is called &quot;perogies&quot; (another try on pierogi), but the in-game item is based on polish version of the dish.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Lunarpromo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Webber and Wickerbottom cooking Pierogi in a Lunar New Year promo image.\"><img alt=\"Webber and Wickerbottom cooking Pierogi in a Lunar New Year promo image.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lunarpromo.png/120px-Lunarpromo.png?b50251\" width=\"120\" height=\"66\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Webber\" title=\"Webber\">Webber</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wickerbottom\" title=\"Wickerbottom\">Wickerbottom</a> cooking Pierogi in a Lunar New Year promo image.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_perogies.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_perogies.png/120px-CD_perogies.png?6c0c7b\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Pierogi_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pierogi_128x128.png/120px-Pierogi_128x128.png?e93ae7\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
